                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17150713-6-off29 t17150713-6-cd30"></join> last. The Prosecutor swore, That being a North Britain, and a Stranger in these Parts, the Prisoner got into Talk with him at <placeName id="t17150713-6-crimeloc31">Billingsgate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17150713-6-crimeloc31" type="placeName" value="Billingsgate"></interp>
